            <h3><a href="#"  data-metrics='{"action":"Toggle Footer Dropdown","label":"About","category":"The Salt"}' >About</a></h3>
      <div id="footer_module" class="agglocation linkLocation">
                  <div id="res163939792" class="bucketwrap listtext">
                        <div class="bucket">
                              <p>With a pinch of skepticism and a dash of fun, <em>The Salt </em>covers food news from the farm to the plate and beyond. You can connect with senior editor and host Maria Godoy, or editors Eliza Barclay and April Fulton, <a href="http://help.npr.org/npr/includes/customer/npr/custforms/contactus.aspx?sid=70">via our contact form</a> or directly by <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&tf=1&to=thesalt@npr.org">email</a>.</p>
